        <detaileddescription>
<para>adds triangles along the boundary to straighten it;</para>
<para>new triangle is added only if 1) aspect ratio of the new triangle is at most maxTriAspectRatio, 2) dot product of its normal with neighbor triangles is at least minNeiNormalsDot. </para>
